Package tools.data.img

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoundedImageSheet
    Image sheet abstract implementation for bounded image sheets.
    DefaultGUIImageSheet
    This class is a default implementation of a GUI image sheet which uses custom images.
    GUIImageSheet
    Interface for an image sheet getter for the tools.gui package.
    ImageSheet
    Interface for image sheets.
    ManagedGUIImageSheet
    This GUI image sheet provides a basic setup for when using managed sheets as source.
    ManagedImageSheet
    Image sheet implementation which uses image sheet arrays from the ImageManager class.
    ModImageSheet  
    OverlayImageSheet
    Image sheet which adds the images on top of each other.
    QuadrupleGUIImageSheet
    The default image sheet collection for GUI applications.
    SingleGUIImageSheet
    Implementation of the GUIImageSheet class which returns a single sheet for all states of the button.
    SourceImageSheet
    Image sheet class for using a raw image sheet as source.
    SubImageSheet
    Bounded image sheet class which creates a translated sub-view from another image sheet.
